_json.gridTitle: Planning A Retreat in 8 Steps | The Free Woman
_json.description: There is not a more accurate picture of joy and merriment than a group of girlfriends having a good time. Every woman needs a community of friends she can call up at any time, laugh with about silly things and celebrate the beauty of womanhood. But sometimes the chaos of daily life prevents women from spending wholesome, uninterrupted time together; friends may find it difficult to catch up without distractions and worries pressing in.
